* D kept his eyes trained on Vlad, glancing down at his little wolf-dog as 
she walked up and seemed to nuzzle Fenox for attention.
In his mind it was only natural for females to recognize each other so it 
didn't bother him, but Vlad did.
D was new there but Fenox had been the first person he met and was nice to 
him so he felt it his duty to watch out for her and protect her, even though 
his beast mode senses tried to take over sometimes and made him possessive 
of her.
D took in a breath and let it out quickly as Fenox have him a reasuring pet, 
not moving and his eyes still triened on Vlad.
He just didn't trust him.
But it made D growl again when he looked at Fenox again and saw her smiling 
at him, making him feel possessive again and bare his teeth at Vlad.*
